The paper also discusses the use of a publicly available benchmark dataset for evaluation purposes, which falls under the category of software engineering. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a likely category. 

The paper also discusses the use of load signatures and feature spaces, which falls under the category of signal processing. Therefore, cs.SD (Signal Processing) is also a likely category. 

Finally, the paper discusses the use of load signatures for energy disaggregation, which falls under the category of energy and power systems. Therefore, cs.NE (Networks and Energy) is also a likely category.
